Package: blsmarks
Type: Package
Title: Enter Grades into NTU BLS Marks Excel Spreadsheets
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Mark", "Andrews",
      email = "mark.andrews@ntu.ac.uk",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: All student grades for BLS in NTU must be entered into Excel Spreadsheets created by BLS Student Records.
  This package provides an R function to transfer student grades from a data from into these spreadsheets.
License: GPL (>= 3)
